{
  "stem": "9538.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I go for a walk here in the park and I see a dog, people must think, oh, there's a mad woman there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I can't-- I sort of--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It goes back a long way, but I should know better by now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we lived under terrifically bad conditions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no running water-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to wash in a lake.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The SS girls took us to the lake.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the lake by that time had frozen over, and we had to knock a hole into the lake for us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they insisted that we undressed ourselves and washed ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's where we stayed there, until Christmas of '44, when suddenly we had to march out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know where and what.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those who had still survived were assembled, marched out of the gates accompanied by SS men and SS women and the commandant, who-- they drove in a car, but we marched and the SS.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And wherever we walked, however many miles we walked, we saw different groups coming-- also prisoners that worked in different places.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we all marched one direction because the Russian front was coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians were coming in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, Riga was-- I heard later on-- Riga was already liberated, and the whole of Latvia was already liberated from the Germans who were pushed out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came then nearer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's why they wanted to get rid of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they marched us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The conditions, I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Somebody said eventually we were-- we were 3,000.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we marched for six weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At night, they drove us into forest-- during the day, they drove us into forests so that people shouldn't see us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at night, we marched.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How can you sleep?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
